'''Stephen Gallagher''' is a New Zealand composer and music editor. He worked as a music editor for [[The Hobbit (film series)|''The Hobbit'' film series]]. For ''[[The Hobbit: An Unexpected Journey]]'', Gallagher also composed music for [[Blunt the Knives]] sung by the [[Thorin and Company|Dwarves]] and The Torture Song sung by the [[Great Goblin|Goblin King]].<ref name="SGAbout">{{webcite|articleurl=https://stephengallagher.co.nz/about/|articlename=About|dated=|website=[https://stephengallagher.co.nz/ Stephen Gallagher]|accessed=5 February 2023}}</ref> He composed the score for the animated film ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The War of the Rohirrim]]''.<ref>{{webcite|articleurl=https://twitter.com/moviescorewire/status/1621949825959825408|articlename=MovieScore Wire|dated=4 February 2023|website=[https://twitter.com Twitter]|accessed=5 February 2023}}</ref>

